      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, currently maintained in a state of aesthetic and mechanical perfection. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a machine that has been preserved to an exacting standard, showing no signs of compromise or wear. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, every detail confirms a history of meticulous stewardship. This is an acquisition for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than the pinnacle of pre-owned excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
